{"tid":862924,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想養隻英短","createTime":"2018-10-15T08:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T13:55:54.000Z","uid":203172,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ed7ccf9b30b419c501074b12e8c4eeae89041732","tid":862924,"uid":203172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T08:39:57.000Z","msg":"想養隻忌廉色英短女 最好就三個月左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊間貓舍係正規同有良心？貴啲唔緊要 只係想貓貓健健康康 有咩遺傳病唔單止睇獸醫貴 見到佢辛苦都好肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企隻主子就係遺傳病耳仔有事 冇得醫 見佢辛苦都好心痛 所以更加唔想買到病貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知道一定有領養撚入黎屌鳩我買貓 如果你搵到有忌廉色三個月大英短女我狗衝去領養翻黎 真心<br />\n睇過曬fb 啲寵物交易區 但好多都係私人ac 唔知可唔可信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  各位Ching 有冇相熟breeder 或者信譽良好嘅貓舍可以推介？木星貓舍係咪真係貴得有道理？<br />\n唔該曬各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11566c9750a462481bfa8e979d749aec9f2b4885","tid":862924,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:04:39.000Z","msg":"咪害人啦"},{"pid":"73f37579a4c57a2b409e9c92dbd115863997f5cf","tid":862924,"uid":115593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:53:51.000Z","msg":"木星啲貓好似唔會三個月就接得<br />\n我阿女都差唔多成四個月<br />\n（我阿女係比較肥同大隻）<br />\n同埋佢一定要打哂兩針<br />\n<br />\n同埋英短啲腸胃都比較差啲<br />\n會屙下爛同血便<br />\n<br />\n其實除左佢仲有其他breeder<br />\n你都可以睇下"},{"pid":"6da730b6af0385cf2c6e5b5aaf9f5c35f2e5e6c1","tid":862924,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"撞手神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a129a52dd494d1ea7eb390b9fe13c3b862189b57","